title: Trisha & Ethan Got Bullied - Frenemies # 36
description: On this episode of Frenemies Ethan & Trisha fight back against a bunch of mean ol' internet cyber bullies who have a lot to say about our favorite duo! We also discuss Ethan's trip to Vegas, Robin Williams, and a whole lot more!!!
